Contains ALL results saved out from R-Scripts

- Contains all the splitted data (folds, training, testing)
- Contains the four different recipes
- Contains all the eleven fits/models
- Contains the best paramaters and their corresponding RMSE values for each model
- Contains the table of all RMSE values (RMSE_table.rda)
- Contains the final fit onto the winning model (final_fit.rda)
- Contains the predictions made onto the testing data (final_predict.rda)
- Contains the evaluation of the final model on other performance metrics (RMSE, R^2, and MAE) (evaluation_table.rda)
- Contains scatterplot of the predicted values vs the actual values (scatterplot.rda)
